sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Application
    participant libpq as libpq (fe-exec.c)
    participant PG as Postgres (copyfrom.c)

    Note over App, PG: Initial Command Phase
    App->>libpq: PQexec("COPY table FROM STDIN")
    libpq->>PG: Query(COPY FROM...)
    PG->>PG: Parse & Plan (CopyStmt)
    PG-->>libpq: PGRES_COPY_IN (Ready to receive)
    libpq-->>App: Return PGresult

    Note over App, PG: Streaming Phase (COPY State)
    loop until all data sent
        App->>libpq: PQputCopyData(buffer)
        libpq->>PG: CopyData chunk
        PG->>PG: Data parsing & Tuple formation
        PG->>PG: Insert into target relation
    end

    Note over App, PG: Termination Phase
    App->>libpq: PQputCopyEnd(NULL)
    libpq->>PG: CopyDone
    PG->>PG: Flush buffers & Update indexes
    PG-->>libpq: CommandComplete (rows inserted)
    libpq-->>App: Final Result
